  "texts": [
    "The rib cage of a person may be seen with CXR.",
    "The CXR approach is typically the primary choice if radiologists can identify the chest pathology.",
    "Considering the circumstance, the COVID-19 is detected using the CXR technique [7,8].",
    "As a result, the only focus of this study is on utilising X-ray imaging to identify COVID-19 patients in the future.The development of automatic detection methods based on artificial intelligence is required due to the rapid expansion of the COVID-19 pandemic.",
    "It is challenging to locate skilled physicians for each institution because of the shortage of skilled radiologists in various locations."
  ]
